1521	// Drives zrbld_spine_validate — the Lode capture-assembly spine's dispatch-time
1522	// substitution-coverage check — directly: write a substitution-keys file and an
1523	// already-include-expanded step body, source buv_validation + rblds_spine and
1524	// kindle buv so buc_log_args resolves, then assert the check accepts a fully
1525	// covered body and returns non-zero at the first _RBGL_* reference absent from
1526	// the keys. The check is sentinel-free and reads only its two file arguments, so
1527	// this stays a dependency-free unit test — no rbld kindle, no regime, no creds.
1528	
1529	fn rbtdrf_rc_run(
1530	    dir: &Path,
1531	    label: &str,
1532	    keys: &str,
1533	    body: &str,
1534	    expect_ok: bool,
